/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created:     14 March 2003		cnwth2	
//
// Purpose:     		 
//
// Changed		By			Reason
// ----------   ----------  --------------------------------------------------
// 02/12/2009	cnwdap1		CCMS MES 1007 moved reefer properties from CM_Container to CM_TrackedItem
